Hello, this is 6-minute English from BBC Learning English. I'm Neil.

3
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.400
And I'm Beth.

4
00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:15.720
In this program, we'll be discussing the dinner table.

5
00:00:15.720 --> 00:00:21.000
But we're not interested in food. We're talking about talking.

6
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:23.720
A lot can happen around the dinner table.

7
00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:29.720
Arguments, you might meet the love of your life on a blind dinner date.

8
00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:32.720
Or find out you're a great storyteller.

9
00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:36.720
